This swanky cocktail bar offers these cocktails – Elderflower Spritz, Flamingo, and Savoy Cooler – at S$14 each (U.P. S$22); as well as three types of wines – Torresella Prosecco Brut, Pirramimma Chardonnay, and Tamar Ridge Pinot Noir – at $S14 each (U.P. S$17).

101 Amoy Street
Singapore 069921
Nearest Station: Telok Ayer
